Since the inception of our company in 1996,
 we have been pioneers in the domain, with a number of innovations and 
groundbreaking products under our belt. Backed by a posse of qualified 
engineers, exceptional designers and highly experienced marketing 
personnel, we have established ourselves as a noted Manufacturer, Exporter and Supplier of products such as Polymer, Plastic, LLDPE, Grinding Pulverizer Machine  and LDPE Pulverizer Machines to name a few.

Advantages

No brand in the market even comes close to the features and usage benefits offered by the VDM range of pulverizers offered by Vedanta Machineries Pvt. Ltd.,
 whose exceptional performance is in a league of their own. Following 
are a few noteworthy advantages that are associated with our product 
offerings: 

Hassle free adjustment of blade gaps with high accuracy
Less power hungry components, high energy efficiency, leading to increased productivity
Relatively compact design that saves considerable amount of space
Comparatively less material time in grinding and related purposes, thus, multiplying the gross output
A much higher output can be obtained if the material to be pulverized is at a temperature below the melting point
An expansive range to choose from, with various models available in different technical specifications
A cosmopolitan design, suited for polymers of all types
An advanced air cooling system used, thereby negating the need the conventional and less efficient water cooling mechanism

