					            About Vedanta Ltd.Vedanta Ltd., incorporated in the year 1965, is a Large Cap company (having a market cap of ₹ 102111.33 Cr.) operating in Mining sector. Vedanta Ltd. key Products/Revenue Segments include Minerals which contributed ₹ 37344.67 Cr to Sales Value (96.89 % of Total Sales), Mining/Minerals which contributed ₹ 37344.67 Cr to Sales Value (96.89 % of Total Sales), Job Work which contributed ₹ 752.65 Cr to Sales Value (1.95 % of Total Sales), Export Incentives which contributed ₹ 155.14 Cr to Sales Value (0.40 % of Total Sales), Other Operating Revenue which contributed ₹ 148.89 Cr to Sales Value (0.38 % of Total Sales), Sale of services which contributed ₹ 92.41 Cr to Sales Value (0.23 % of Total Sales), Scrap which contributed ₹ 31.58 Cr to Sales Value (0.08 % of Total Sales), Slag which contributed ₹ 11.96 Cr to Sales Value (0.03 % of Total Sales) and Service Charges which contributed ₹ 3.12 Cr to Sales Value (0.00 % of Total Sales)for the year ending 31-Mar-2017.For the quarter ended 30-06-2017, the company has reported a  Consolidated sales of ₹ 19342.00 Cr., down -14.08 from last quarter Sales of ₹ 22511.27 Cr. and up 34.66 from last year same quarter Sales of ₹ 14364.01 Cr. Company has reported net profit after tax of ₹ 2270.00 Cr. in latest quarter.The company’s top management includes Mr.Aman Mehta, Mr.Anil Agarwal, Mr.G R Arun Kumar, Mr.K Venkataramanan, Mr.Navin Agarwal, Mr.Ravi Kant, Mr.Tarun Jain, Mr.Thomas Albanese, Ms.Lalita Gupte, Ms.Priya Agarwal. Company has S R Batliboi & Co. LLP as its auditors. As on 30-06-2017, the company has a total of 3,717,194,239 shares outstanding.View Details:Chairman's SpeechCompany HistoryDirectors ReportBackground informationCompany ManagementListing InformationFinished ProductsBoard MeetingsAGM/EGMClose XAlertWatchlistPortfolioCurrent Price: 2389.88Lower LimitUpper LimitSet AlertTo continue receiving alerts, please enter your email id below:Enter email address:SubmitAdd this company to your 