Vedanta Ltd: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















vedanta ltd
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Materials
Industry: Metals & Mining
Sub-Industry: Base Metals
Vedanta Limited mines, produces, and exports base metals. The Company distributes metals such as zinc, iron ore, copper, silver, and aluminium, as well as operates power plants. Vedanta also operates in oil and gas sector.




